I"H<h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>

<p>The Account API enables you to make a password reset request for a user.</p>

<h2 id="password-reset">Password reset</h2>

<p>You can create a request for password reset by issuing a http <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">POST</code> to the following url:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>https://api.eet.nu/password_resets/:email
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>If the email is not found or incorrect, the API returns a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">404 Not Found</code> status header. If the password request has been created, a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">201 Created</code> status will be returned with an empty response body.
:email is case-insensitive.</p>
:ET